snippet.title: Meghan Markle humiliated as public fail to honor birthday plea: A Huge Learning Moment!
snippet.description:
MEGHAN MARKLE turned 40 and to mark the milestone, she asked her fans to share a birthday poem on Instagram, however just over 200 public accounts have honored the plea. I talk about Samantha and Thomas Jr. Markle's voice  can help counter the PR stunts of Sussex Royal. This should have been a huge learning lesson for Meghan and her public relations team. 


SOURCE: https://www.express.co.uk/news/royal/1473145/meghan-markle-birthday-instagram-40x40-melissa-mccarthy-video-prince-harry-royal-news
